event.eventaddress: Humboldt Park, 3000 S Howell Ave, Milwaukee, WI
event.eventbdesc: Hare Krishna Temple booth at IndiaFest

eventldesc.para1: Come visit our Stall at Humboldt Park during the IndiaFest festival. Temple has organized Kritan and Free Food to all.
eventldesc.para2: We shall have Kirtan and spread the name of Hare Krishna.
eventldesc.para3: Hare Krishna Hare Krishna Krishna Krishna Hare Hare, Hare Rama Hare Rama Rama Rama Hare Hare.
eventldesc.para4: Looking forward at the event for our little ones, who will enjoy the fun filled atmosphere. This is a FREE event open to all.
